    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. Can you go into more detail about the hair and grooming part? I have some clients who might have different hair textures or styles, so what specific advice would you give to ensure they don't look \"unprofessional\" or \"distracting\" in that setting?",
      "source": "evaluator"
